public class VocabMain

Runs the Latin Vocab Helper. Notes: With the advent of the new system, the user will soon be able to create a "missed words" txt file (actually made by program by compiling his mistakes) so that he only is quizzed on those words. Also, since the user picks the files, he can create new files himself and then run the Vocab Helper with them. Thus, almost anything can be tested. !!!
